title: Emily Ratajkowski and Hailey Baldwin at NYFW dinner | Daily Mail Online
text: Share 90 shares Emily wore her dark locks loose while rocking brown shadow on her lids with nude lipstick. Hailey put her perky backside on display in the clingy dress. A vision! Hailey, 20, put her perky backside on display in the clingy dress The peach short-sleeved number was fitted along the torso and derriere but flared out at the bottom. Hailey's look included a corset, emphasizing her tiny waist. She styled her chic look with pointed cream heels, hoop earrings and wore her blond locks into a top knot. Flawless: Emily, 25, chose a halter dress that had plunging sides and an open back; the number also featured a thigh-high slit Having a laugh: The dark haired beauty wowed in her lace-up black heels that grazed her lower thighs; Emily pictured with Harley Viera-Newton Like a glove: The peach short-sleeved number was fitted along the torso and derriere but flared out at the bottom; it also had a corset detail Hailey rocked copper eye makeup with shimmering blush and defined brows. Hours before the dinner, the blonde beauty shared two revealing snaps to her Instagram. In one photo, Hailey rocked a blush glittering set, showing off her svelte frame. Earlier in the day, the model posted another picture; she wore a sparkling top with a black skirt. Hailey captioned it: 'I'm always tired in fittings.'
